  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set to 3. Ten of thirteen credibility factors are assessed; three factors — Numerical solver error, Use error, and Equivalency of input parameters — are marked not-assessed with rationale citing scope constraints. Because MRL 3 exceeds the threshold at which unassessed factors materially weaken credibility, this package embeds weakener W-EP-04. The overall decision is recorded as Accepted, masking the epistemic gap.",
