    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the ten assessed factors collectively provide sufficient evidence to support model use at MRL 3 for the VAD hemolysis prediction COU. Three factors (Numerical solver error, Use error, Equivalency of input parameters) were not assessed but were considered beyond the current submission scope. The team concluded that the assessed evidence, combined with Monte Carlo UQ on model inputs, provides adequate confidence for a Low assurance level decision. The not-assessed factors were noted for future work but were not treated as blockers to acceptance.",
